{"title":"Count the number of repetitions of letters, words in the text","description":"This program allows you to find all the repeated characters and words in the text, counts their number and displays them in a convenient table","content":"## Number of repeated characters and words\r\nThis program allows you to find all the repeated characters and words in the text, counts their number and displays them in a convenient table. To get statistics on a certain part of the text, it is enough to highlight it - the information will be quickly updated and displayed in the table.\n\n You can also familiarize yourself with other functionality of this online [text editor](/en/editor)."}